rdistributed_cacheforratelimitonAPIGateway?andwhatisconfiguredinProduction.=
.">Wanted to know do we use local_cache or distributed_cache for rate limit=
 on API Gateway ? and what is configured in Production..</a></li>
<li><a href=3D"#TPSFrequentlyAskedQuestions-HowdoestheTPSlimitworksonanAPI?=
Doesitconsidertheactivethreadsfromprevioussecond?">How does the TPS limit w=
orks on an API? Does it consider the active threads from previous second?</=
a></li>
